Package: s4p
Type: Package
Title: Test and optimise sampling designs based on plume simulations
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2014-11-18
Author: Kristina B. Helle
Maintainer: Kristina B. Helle <kristina.helle@uni-muenster.de>
Description: With this package you can load plume simulations (on lattice or points), even if it does not fit into memory. Then you can test your sampling designs by several, flexible cost functions -- that usually are based on the simulations. You may also optimise the sampling designs by different optimisation algorithms.
License: GPL-3
Depends: gstat, sp, raster
Imports: rgdal, FNN, methods, graphics, conf.design, automap, genalg
Suggests: testthat
